{
  "_comment": "Canonical haunting platform config — kiro-cli sessions. Uses run.sh dispatcher pattern: on rocm-aibox executes locally, on other machines SSH-tunnels. docker-mcp removed (broken on Linux Engine). Paths relative to hauntingkirocli repo root.",
